# Implementation Plan - Phase 7: Automated Outreach Integration

This phase focuses on empowering the platform with automated communication capabilities, allowing users to create multi-channel outreach campaigns (Email/WhatsApp) targeting leads with high AI scores.

## Proposed Changes

### Database Architecture
Group: Data Persistence

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/prisma/schema.prisma)
*   Add `OutreachCampaign` model to handle group outreach settings.
*   Add `OutreachMessage` model to track individual delivery status and performance (read/delivered).
*   Add relations to [Tenant](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/app/api/leads/ingest/route.ts#22-29) and [Lead](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/components/admin/LeadsDataTable.tsx#18-66).

---

### Orchestration Engine
Group: Backend Services

#### [NEW] `src/lib/outreach/outreach-service.ts`
*   Core service to handle campaign execution.
*   Integrates with [mail.ts](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/lib/mail.ts) (Resend) and [whatsapp-client.ts](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/lib/meta/whatsapp-client.ts).
*   Includes a `processQueue` method to handle scheduled or throttled sending.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/outreach/campaigns/route.ts` & `[id]/route.ts`
*   CRUD operations for outreach campaigns.
*   Endpoints to enroll leads into specific campaigns.

---

### Campaign Management UI
Group: Admin Dashboard

#### [NEW] `src/app/admin/outreach/page.tsx`
*   Main dashboard for viewing campaign performance (conversion rates, open rates).
*   List of active/completed campaigns.

#### [NEW] `src/app/admin/outreach/new/page.tsx`
*   Multi-step form to create campaigns:
    1.  Select Channel (Email/WhatsApp).
    2.  Define Sequence/Template (using AI-generated content as a base).
    3.  Select Audience (Filtering by Tier or Score).

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
*   **Unit Tests**: Test `OutreachService` with mocked mail/whatsapp providers.
*   **API Tests**: Validate campaign creation and lead enrollment flow.

### Manual Verification
*   Create a "Test Campaign" for 5 leads.
*   Verify that messages are created in `PENDING` state.
*   Check that Email (via Resend logs) and WhatsApp (via Meta API) are triggered correctly.
*   Verify status updates in the Lead Drawer.
